ABOUT CLEANECO

Cleaneco is a Dubai-based swimming pool maintenance and water tank cleaning company dedicated to delivering safe, hygienic, and crystal-clear water solutions. We combine professional expertise, eco-conscious practices, and industry-approved methods to ensure the highest standards of cleanliness and safety.

From residential water tanks to commercial swimming pools, our trained team handles every job with precision and care - offering complete draining, deep scrubbing, sediment removal, and thorough disinfection & sanitization. We focus not just on visible cleanliness, but on eliminating hidden contaminants that affect water quality and health.

At Cleaneco, we believe clean water is essential to a healthy lifestyle. That’s why we are committed to reliable service, transparent processes, and results you can trust - every time.

​

​

OUR TEAM & WORK PHILOSOPHY

At Cleaneco, our strength lies in our people. Our team is made up of trained technicians, pool specialists, and water hygiene professionals who share a common goal - delivering safe, spotless, and reliable water solutions.

Each team member brings hands-on experience in swimming pool maintenance and water tank cleaning, supported by ongoing training in modern cleaning techniques, safety standards, and eco-friendly practices. From detailed inspections to precise execution, our crew works with care, discipline, and attention to detail on every site.

What makes our team special is our culture. We believe in teamwork, accountability, and doing the job right the first time. Our work philosophy is simple: treat every pool and water tank as if it were our own. This mindset drives us to go beyond surface cleaning and focus on long-term water hygiene and customer satisfaction.

We value transparency, respect, and consistency - both within our team and with our clients. Whether it’s a residential villa or a commercial facility, our professionals arrive prepared, uniformed, and committed to delivering results you can trust.

At Cleaneco, you’re not just hiring a service - you’re partnering with a team that genuinely cares about clean water and healthier living.
